        "As Partner at SPVH AMC and Fund Manager at the 'SPVH Value Discovery Fund' (a SEBI-registered Category II AIF), Jimit plays a pivotal role in identifying emerging and pre-IPO businesses. His responsibilities encompass evaluating business fundamentals, assessing financial performance, reviewing governance readiness, and coordinating with merchant bankers, legal advisors, and transaction stakeholders.",
