        "At his core, Saurav believes that capital structuring is not standardized but highly tailored, transparent, and aligned with long-term business objectives."
      ],
      specialties: "Investment Banking, Capital Structuring, M&A Advisory, IPO & Capital Markets, Financial Strategy & Restructuring, and Strategic Advisory."
    }
  },
  {
    id: "karan-nagda",
    name: "Karan Nagda",
    role: "Director\nSPVH Group",
    image: "/images/Karan-updated-640-640.webp",
    bio: "",
    quote: "Raising capital is an event; sustaining conviction is an art — one built on insight, timing, and trust.",
    extendedBio: {
      paragraphs: [
        "Karan Nagda serves as a strategic force in capital markets and equity structuring, driving initiatives that navigate complex market environments and unlock long-term enterprise value.",
        "His specialization spans both SME and mainboard IPOs, encompassing comprehensive pre-IPO readiness, strategic valuation positioning, and precise investor alignment.",
        "Drawing upon his extensive expertise in trading, portfolio management, and market execution, he brings a highly disciplined and analytical approach to capital deployment.",
        "Ultimately, his strength lies in his ability to translate capital ambition into structured market outcomes, providing steadfast guidance across the entire lifecycle of a business."
      ],
      specialties: "Capital Markets Strategy, IPO Advisory (SME & Mainboard), Pre-IPO Readiness, Investor Positioning & Valuation, Trading & Portfolio Management, and Market Liquidity & Execution."
    }
  },
  {
    id: "karan-gupta",
    name: "Karan Gupta",
    role: "Partner\nPrivate equity & Venture capital",
    image: "/images/ChatGPT-Image-May-13,-2026,-04_20_10-PM-(1)-1024.webp",
    bio: "Driving private equity investments to nurture and grow businesses into industry leaders."
  },
  {
    id: "saviraj-shetty",
    name: "Saviraj Shetty",
    role: "Managing Director & CEO\nMedia & Entertainment",
