    bio: "Overseeing investments and strategic capital in the dynamic media and entertainment sectors."
  },
  {
    id: "dharam-vora",
    name: "Dharam Vora",
    role: "Partner\nAutomobiles",
    image: "/images/Dharam-updated-640.webp",
    bio: "",
    quote: "However the world changes, one truth stays—arrival commands attention. I help define that moment.",
    extendedBio: {
      paragraphs: [
        "Dharam Vora is Partner – Automobiles at SPVH Group, leading the automotive vertical with a focus on building a scalable, organized, and trust-driven luxury pre-owned car ecosystem.",
